T1  - Constant Consumption and the Economic Depreciation of Natural Capital: The Nonautonomous Case
AU  - Hartwick, John M.
AU  - Van Long, Ngo
Y1  - 1999/02/01
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/1468-2354.00004
T2  - International Economic Review
